long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rank Ranger's Link Manager & Backlink Tracker was built to help professionals who buy, sell or exchange links to efficiently manage and track backlinks.

You work hard to create quality backlinks and supplier relationships, monitor your investment with Rank Ranger's Link management and SEO Metrics tools. 

Track and analyze backlinks, monitor supplier/employee activity & expenses with link and project management tools, review backlink SEO stats & metrics, and more with our powerful Link Management software.   

Check out our full features list at http://www.rankranger.com/link-manager

IMPORTANT: You need to visit http://www.rankranger.com/ and set up your account before using this extension
